### 取得總掛號數
GET http://localhost:8080/api/appointments/count

### 取得所有掛號 (無參數)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/appointments

### 依日期查詢掛號
GET http://localhost:8080/api/appointments?date=1985-03-15

### 統計頁面 (HTML)
GET http://localhost:8080/stats

### 取得總掛號數 API
GET http://localhost:8080/api/appointments/count

### 查詢所有掛號記錄 (無參數)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/appointments

### 依日期篩選掛號 (?date=YYYY-MM-DD)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/appointments?date=2026-05-01

### 依醫師 ID 篩選掛號 (?doctorId=D001)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/appointments?doctorId=D001

### 同時依日期與醫師篩選
GET http://localhost:8080/api/appointments?date=2026-05-01&doctorId=D001

### 依醫師 ID 查詢掛號
GET http://localhost:8080/api/appointments?doctorId=D001

### 取消掛號 (測試 ID 為 1 的掛號)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/appointments/1/status
Content-Type: application/json

{ "status": "CANCELLED" }